wiki.content:
"Gangnam Style" (Korean: 강남스타일, IPA: [kaŋnam sɯtʰail]) is a 2012 Korean pop single by the South Korean rapper PSY. It is praised by some for its humor, catchy rhythm as well as PSY's unusual dance moves. The song was released on July 15, 2012, when it debuted at number one on the Gaon Chart. The music video has been viewed over a billion times as of December 26, 2012, making it YouTube's most watched K-Pop video.
